  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6263617">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6263617/" class="title-link">自由及其幻想</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6263617"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/pipiblues/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2656676-52.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pipiblues/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">qingfan</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-09-05"
      class="main-meta">2013-09-05 15:14:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6263617_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  伯林在《谈话录》里提到，相对于积极自由，他更认可消极自由。在《自由及其背叛》一书里，基本上就是对他所认同的消极自由给出论证和反例。伯林说，“自由的本质是什么？自由的本质从来就是，如你所愿地去选择的能力——你选择它，仅仅因为你自己想这么选，而不是因为有人强逼...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
